Hi Machiavelli, 

Thanks for submitting your request. Confirming we have now made the updates and they are ready for you to review. 

Here is the link: 
https://www.machiavelli.com.au/upcoming-event


Please let us know if you would like any further changes.

Use info from: https://www.agfg.com.au/restaurant/machiavelli-restaurant-2093

Heading: 
Zarella Wine Dinner - Tuesday 9th July

Info for dropdown: 

Join us for an exquisite evening of exceptional wines produced in McLaren Vale by the Zerella family, paired with a delicious menu by Machiavelli. Harnessing family tradition, generations-old skills of working the land and a passion for farming, Zerella produce quality wines that are vegan friendly whilst adhering to organic and biodynamic principles. $120 pp Includes 4 course dinner and 5 matched wines. Bookings are essential.
